<p style="text-align: center;"><span><strong>祝福贵在心</strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span><strong>让我们一起</strong><strong>向</strong><strong></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span><strong>“升学宴”“谢师宴”</strong><strong></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span><strong>说“不”</strong></span></p>
<p><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200819/d2ae3d37d7344d86b8b6c147bb02e9ba.png" /></p>
